{
  "stem": "802.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "First of all, we didn't have any papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of our papers were destroyed, so we couldn't prove anything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the only way we could leave Poland-- they didn't want us there, but they would not let us go, either.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the only way we could do it is to claim that we're born in Austria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So my cousin went to Krakow, and he was able to produce false birth certificates, because we had nothing else.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, in his anxiety and excitement, he-- Well, first of all, we decided that we'll be a family-- a mother and four children-- and that we're all born in Austria.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so, when he made out these birth certificates, in his-- as I said, his tension, he wrote on one of them that my younger cousin was only three or four months older than I.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The date that he gave-- one was born January, one was born in April or some such of the same year.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, we were caught on the border of Poland and Czechoslovakia, where the Poles were.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent us back, so we had to go through the same thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we stayed in some awful places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my cousin went back to Krakow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we couldn't go back in Chorzow, to that apartment, obviously.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyway, I did tell you that the woman did not let them in, right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She bolted the door.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was really quite decent.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And ultimately, we got other papers and were able to pass through the-- the searches and everything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "What do you call it when you pass a border?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There are the, uh-- the officials who are there, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they searched us thoroughly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my mother had already a girdle.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
